oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Frank Tighe's store
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Frank Tighe's store. Also shown is the bank.
Store was in business from the 1930's to the 1960's. These buildings are now behind the present courthouse and the street is no longer there.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
